OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry across the region
OL,6,Ftoday with some early mist patches.
OL,7,FSunny spells at first, but clouding
OL,8,Fover a little during the afternoon,
OL,9,Fwith a small chance of a few showers.
OL,10,FLess windy than Saturday.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAny showers easing to leave a
OL,13,Fdry night. Cloud will break up to give
OL,14,Fsome clear spells. Turning chilly
OL,15,Fwhere skies clear.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FDry at first on Monday with
OL,18,Fsome sunshine. Turning cloudier during
OL,19,Fthe afternoon and breezier as a spell
OL,20,Fof rain arrives later in the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
